            Perhaps I may say to the Minister that. in our discussions on the <a href="/bills/competition-bill">Competition Bill</a>&#x2014;going back some time&#x2014;I did not realise that we had allowed the Secretary of State to have such fantastic power. What happens if the Secretary of State has a brainstorm and goes mad?
