        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0647P0-01629'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0647P0_20030408_GCR_430' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at twenty-eight minutes before eight o'clock.
      </p>
      <ol class='xoxo'>
        
